metadata.name: SINGULARITY
metadata.description:
Digital painting.

Panoramic view of digitally hand sculpted metamorphic architectural space.

Gentle lines hide among intense meshes, flowing freely they create a fabric of space, or maybe a landscape of a distant asteroid from an outer space? We invite you on a journey that explores the idea of architectural space.  

Inspired by the new wave of Web3 technology we want to visualize the landscape of the Metaverse.

Digitally hand sculpted in 3D, the artwork stems from an architectural research in depth.

by MABLAB
